name: Flight’s Geometry: Sunrise for Colombia
description: This is a protection sygil. Paper plane drawing scheme and colorized for SOS Colombia, 2100 × 2970 pixels, 57.950 bytes, RGB Color, PNG Archive, 2021, created under chaos magic principles and donated by @Metachaosphere (https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/tz/tz1Rap5Gv7XEhQbrS1PRqg9R1v9Nojdginq4) to help raise money in solidarity for the protestors in Colombia. —> https://bit.ly/3h1Uk7J 100% of the proceeds will go to support front liners and protestors: https://bit.ly/3haO9i1
